name: Chicken Run! (Fish Taco & Co.)
description:
Made for the Godot wild jam! (Sorry for no html5 export, it is a 3D game so we apologize for the inconvenience).

Play as a curious chicken named Jerlin (he/hen) who needs to save as many of her eggs as possible! Run around the farm gathering eggs by pointing your mouse cursor,  but watch out for the meteors raining down upon you. You will not die from them, but your little babies will. Gather as many baby chickens as possible by the end to get your high score!
